Class MagicStoreProgram

java.lang.Object
com.company.MagicStoreProgram
public class MagicStoreProgram
extends java.lang.Object

Magic Store Program

The MagicStore program implements an application that manages the potions of a Magic Store.
Since:
2019-10-01
